node.text: These past couple weeks have been the craziest of my life. From shooting a movie, to landing and having 2 days to put the entire corvette back together for this campaign, to flying to VIR to test the new @cadillac CT5V Blackwing, flying home for 24 hours to run the C8 at Famoso drag strip yesterday, and now headed back to the airport to fly to Detroit for an exciting opportunity with @chevrolet … I am incredibly grateful. Grateful for every single one of you for believing in me. I’m often told my work ethic is crazy, but i believe my dreams are crazier.

node.text:
Have some BIG news to share with you all this tomorrow, which also happens to be my birthday (edit: announcement will be made August 2nd) !! It wasn’t planned to be announced then, but I’m flying home for 24 hours to share the news with you and I’m so excited. 

Thankful to surround myself with some pretty amazing people like my good friend @jonescrow 🙌🏼 thank you for being a part of this project… Can’t wait to share with you all!!

And yes I’m jealous of Jones being able to park cars in his living room 😅

node.text:
So incredibly thankful to be a part of such an awesome project with some pretty incredible people. @laurenswickard thank you for trusting me with a role in your movie!! 
Lauren is such an inspiration to me. She wrote and co produced A California Christmas which was the number 1 movie in the world for 2 weeks running last year, had a kid after filming, while pregnant wrote a sequel, and 3 months after having her first newborn is back on set producing and starring in her next film 🙌🏼 
Director @directorshaunpiccinino is also such a blessing to work with and he and @bradrushingdp have beautiful talent and eye for really make these scenes come to life. 
@aliafsharesx and ESX Productions is the glue that holds this family together ❤️ I’m not crying you’re crying 😭 Thank you crew and everyone who’s a part of this project, I can’t wait to share with you all!
